After Ubuntu VM installation run the following command to udpate the packages
sudo apt-get udpate
Install SSH with the followign command "sudo apt install ssh"
Install Python3 on Ubuntu with the following command "apt install python3"
Install Pip with the following command "apt install python3-pip"
pip install pytest pytest-clarity pyyaml tabulate jinja2 textfsm pexpect netmiko graphviz
apt-get install graphviz
